Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:41.38,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}隨波逐流而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:44.53,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便天涯兩隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:47.13,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便身無一物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.41,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只得背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:53.64,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}念你如初
