Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:22.43,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只要你還活在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:26.11,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:30.96,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}我就不會容許這片土地淪陷
